```plantuml
@startuml alfredcs_immersion_day_labs

actor User
participant "SageMaker Studio" as Studio
participant "SageMaker Training" as Training
participant "SageMaker Endpoint" as Endpoint
participant "S3 Bucket" as S3
participant "Feature Store" as FS
participant "Hugging Face Hub" as HF

User -> Studio: Initiates ML workflow
Studio -> S3: Uploads training data
Studio -> HF: Pulls pre-trained model
Studio -> Training: Launches training job with\nconfig (instance type, hyperparams)
Training -> S3: Reads training data
Training -> HF: Downloads model weights
Training -> Training: Fine-tunes model\n(using Trainer API/optimizations)
Training -> S3: Saves trained model artifacts
Training --> Studio: Training completion notification

Studio -> Endpoint: Deploys model\n(real-time/batch config)
Endpoint -> S3: Loads model artifacts
Endpoint --> Studio: Endpoint ready confirmation

User -> Endpoint: Sends inference request
Endpoint -> Endpoint: Processes request\n(dynamic batching if enabled)
Endpoint -> FS: Optional: Retrieves features
FS --> Endpoint: Returns feature data
Endpoint --> User: Returns prediction results

@enduml
```